original_title: Crabb Revival: Live at Oak Tree
overview: Captured live at Tennessee's historic studio and venue, the Live at Oak Tree series features enthralling performances from country and southern gospel greats. This installment features the family legacy group Crabb Revival, spotlighting the group's dynamic harmonies and beautiful arrangements on a selection of southern gospel anthems, standards, and hidden gems.
title: Crabb Revival: Live at Oak Tree
